results.name: Let a(n,m) = card{f^(n) : f is a mapping from a set of m elements into itself}, where f^(l)(x) = f^(l-1)(f(x)),l>0, f^(0)(x) = x; sequence gives a(n,5).
comment: Sequence appears to have a rational o.g.f. - _Ralf Stephan_, May 18 2007
